Titolo: Dirt 5

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Dirt 5 (stylised as DIRT 5) is a simcade racing video game developed and published by Codemasters. The game was released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on 6 November 2020, for Xbox Series X/S on 10 November, and for PlayStation 5 on 12 November (for North America, Oceania, Japan, and South Korea) and 19 November (for most other regions), and for Stadia on 24 March 2021. It was the last video game released by Codemasters as an independent company before acquired by former rival Electronic Arts on 18 February 2021.